11. ctmodel - CTA counts cube modelling
---------------------------------------
The get_obs() method, that has been accidently removed, has been put back
which allows computation of a model cube for a stacked analysis. Another
bug was corrected that led to the generation of model cubes with a single
pixel, related to an internal change of the logic in how input information
was handled. This fixes issue #1609.


